{"tid":183547,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「懶人基金」出台後數十基金減價 積金局料情況會持續","createTime":"2017-04-02T07:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T08:19:18.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d58ea7005dbc8eac4245e3977b2055461d9bee3","tid":183547,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170402/large/1491115802_c863.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170402%2Flarge%2F1491115802_c863.jpg&h=963428d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俗稱「懶人基金」的預設投資策略（Default Investment Strategy，簡稱DIS）4月1日推出，積金局機構事務總局執行董事鄭恩賜出席公開活動時表示，法例通過以來，有數十個MPF基金已減價，預計情況會持續，但相信市場需要時間調節，現階段難以估計有多少基金減價。他指會在預設投資通知期限屆滿後視乎反應，再作檢討。<br />\n<br />\n鄭恩賜表示，局方去年已經開始宣傳「懶人基金」，接下來的數月會繼續通知市民有關事宜。他強調預設投資的比例安排是由國際專家經驗得出，認為投資可以在未接近退休時進取一點，踏入50歲後風險就逐步減少。<br />\n<br />\n61萬個從沒作投資指示的MPF賬戶今個月內將收到受託人寄出的通知書，若僱員在指定限期前沒向受託人作出投資指示，其累積及日後新存入的強積金便會自動撥入DIS，投資風險隨時大幅提高。積金局提醒僱員若想繼續沿用現行投資方案須主動通知受託人，勿誤以為不回覆便等於維持不變。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56512769&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56512769%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170402&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=17d17656\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56512769%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170402&h=85979640\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56512769&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170402</a>"},{"pid":"bb713a20b8027f03bf4ccf623d83e717c40c3ebd","tid":183547,"uid":23814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T07:51:49.000Z","msg":"乜撚野出台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d9125541e8b13047c97534441248c6d0e349f9","tid":183547,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T08:19:18.000Z","msg":"俾我拿來炒美國股票同衍生工具好過la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}